    <string-array name="home_quotes">
        <item>Everyone already heard \"Time is money\", so when you are giving your time for those time wasting apps, you\'re actually giving them your most precious and valuable currency for free. So here we are creating a way for you to really see the value of your time, and help everyone willing to take a step further to break free from this \"free time giving addiction\" and take the control again.</item>
        <item>The key is not spending time, but investing it. Every minute you reclaim from distraction is a minute returned to your own story.</item>
        <item>Attention is the rarest and purest form of generosity. Stop giving it away for free.</item>
        <item>Your time is your life. How you spend your hours is how you spend your years.</item>
        <item>The apps are designed to keep you scrolling. You are designed for something greater. Take the control back.</item>
    </string-array>
